Information We Collect and how it is used.

Information We Get When You Use Our Services.

    Camera and Photos information. 

Our application requires to collect images and other information from your device camera and photos. We need this access to take photos for cards, etc., and we can do this only after you give us your consent.

    Usage Information. 

We collect information about your activity within our application. For example, we may collect information about styles or categories which you use to apply to photos, which features you use more often, which fonts and stickers are in demand for you. We need this specific information for statistics which helps us to understand your needs better and which leads us to better improvements of the application. Knowing this information also gives us clues which help to fix possible malfunctions in work of the application.

    Information about applications installed on you device. 

We get information about KVADGroup applications - Photo Studio, Camera+ or others our applications installed on your device in order to implement integration of these applications with eCards.
We also collect information about social networking applications installed on your device to make possible easy sharing of created cards into one of these applications.

    Device Information. 

We collect the information about the type of mobile device you use, your mobile operating system, language, wireless network. We collect this information for general statistics which helps us to improve development and target orientation to users of different groups.

